multiple intracranial recurrences, the proximal cause of death was progressive 
extracranial disease and complications related to pulmonary metastases. Herein, 
we review potential mechanisms of ECM with an emphasis upon glioblastoma 
molecular and genetic profiles and the potential implications of targeted agents 
such as bevacizumab.

