JiaoTong University School of Medicine (SJTU), Chinese Society of Endocrinology 
and Chinese Endocrinologist Association and Wiley Publishing Asia Pty Ltd.

DOI: 10.1111/1753-0407.12326
PMID: 26201444 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


